{"tid":981563,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣民進黨質疑順豐速運\"陸資\"扮\"港資\"","createTime":"2019-01-14T11:35:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-15T03:34:50.000Z","uid":35790,"like":67,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"39de68a0d5777a7383278392e2ae336387a83bfe","tid":981563,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T11:35:42.000Z","msg":"民進黨質疑陸資扮港資<br />\n<br />\n2019-01-14,<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】創辦於1993年的順豐速運，1996年進軍香港物流業，2007年進軍台灣市場，據稱目前在兩岸間快遞業務巿場佔有率達七成。台灣順豐一直強調是「港資」，但民進黨曾指台灣順豐實際上是「陸資」，並擔心順豐發展有可能壟斷台灣貨運業，未來或承攬國防部軍需武器運輸，造成國家安全問題。<br />\n<br />\n負責人為王衛妻子<br />\n<br />\n在國民黨執政時的2014年4月，台灣立法院審議由陸委會提交的「兩岸簽署服貿協議之國家安全審查機制及運作」專案報告。民進黨立委邱議瑩質疑，號稱港資來台投資的「台灣順豐速運」，創辦人兼總裁王衛已將國籍從香港轉為中國深圳市民，並公告由國有企業深圳招商局集團、蘇州元禾控股一起入股順豐速運，取得總計不超過25%股權。她批評經濟部仍認定台灣順豐為港資，擔心兩岸服貿條例通過後，大陸很多資金會以入股的方式併吞台灣產業。<br />\n<br />\n經濟部次長卓士昭答覆時堅持順豐是港資，又指台灣順豐登記的負責人是王衛的妻子，因此經濟部認定順豐速運是港資。資料顯示，王衛的妻子在香港科技大學畢業，她的作風較丈夫更低調，從未在公眾場合出現。<br />\n■記者陳嘯軒<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190114/20590580\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190114%2F20590580&d=e3TO9ons5iEXHyTzMAd6wROFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=e9b99ff0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190114%2F20590580&h=0496f125\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190114/20590580</a>"},{"pid":"af018c86c5b5be461927b01cb9d6214d796f3218","tid":981563,"uid":35790,"like":31,"dislike":1,"score":30,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T11:37:44.000Z","msg":"有香港身份證就係港資<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc46a503ef1be8d7205eb6b2b874df65eb9113be","tid":981563,"uid":33477,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T11:37:45.000Z","msg":"南海中標台北雙子星 台北：于品海是港資不是中資<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/972575\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/972575</a><br />\n于品海都係港資啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n民進黨政府覺得冇問題先最神奇"},{"pid":"ad23515227bcee1eaee4a0c95afd934c8bee531c","tid":981563,"uid":102336,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T11:38:48.000Z","msg":"一路都係支資"},{"pid":"a73c083610404586242def8d2581543bc2b5b841","tid":981563,"uid":19287,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T11:40:36.000Z","msg":"有冇咁蠢dllm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f71c9b8c5d7e2b553ba41dfad1bb9ebb5a6941f","tid":981563,"uid":35790,"like":34,"dislike":1,"score":33,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T11:46:40.000Z","msg":"台灣有d人好on車<br />\n仲停留係97年前英殖民地<br />\n根本現在港資就即係陸資"},{"pid":"a15be650222e9907d5ae2f1c4d07465dbd7d6a93","tid":981563,"uid":28765,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T11:48:36.000Z","msg":"台灣人咁天真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ec634ccfdc3dc81c1503d3d5dae7a3e95fab344","tid":981563,"uid":33848,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T11:50:43.000Z","msg":"幾撚時港資過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1618ca8f24a1d730839f94529c45282fdf08390b","tid":981563,"uid":82640,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T11:51:44.000Z","msg":"台灣人用開IE上網<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f526ffcc5e4280906cf7d428a87fea2dbf61ed38","tid":981563,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T11:51:46.000Z","msg":"深圳係總部同Hub 自己諗掂啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed71b92b40324f6e0a9ad6776e12ec406719a6f8","tid":981563,"uid":126731,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a15be650222e9907d5ae2f1c4d07465dbd7d6a93","tid":981563,"uid":28765,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T11:48:36.000Z","msg":"台灣人咁天真<img src=\